    <stitle>AIR COMPRESSOR: BENDIX TU-FLO 550 AND TU-FLO 750 - ASSEMBLE - PISTONS AND CONNECTING RODS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="assemble" graphiccount="1">
        <title>PISTONS AND CONNECTING RODS</title>
        <para>If the pistons are to be replaced, ensure that the correct pistons are being installed. Note that the
            pistons for the Tu-Flo 550 and 750 compressor are similar to each other and those of other Bendix compressor
            models. They may be identified by the piston diameter and the distance to the center of the wrist pin from
            the top of the piston (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0400315">Figure 15</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <figure id="f0400315" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg04/g0400315.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 15. Piston Comparison</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
